data.description: This property stands out with its assumable loan, available to third parties without the need for VA eligibility, offering a low 2.75% interest rate. Bank documents are uploaded and visible in the MLS. This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home offers covered porch and patio, a spacious kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and a main bedroom suite located downstairs. The primary bathroom offers double vanities, separate tub and shower and a walk-in closet. The second floor includes a large game room, a second full bathroom, and three spacious bedrooms. Additional features include a two-car garage, plumbing in place for water softener and a full irrigation system.
